00:06:12.839 --> 00:06:13.519
Darling.

00:06:13.980 --> 00:06:14.779
The doctor said

00:06:15.100 --> 00:06:15.819
I might

00:06:15.819 --> 00:06:16.899
never regain my vision.

00:06:17.259 --> 00:06:18.379
