00:06:18.540 --> 00:06:19.259
will be entrusted

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:20.360
to you.

00:06:20.899 --> 00:06:21.540
Don't worry.

00:06:21.639 --> 00:06:22.439
I'll always be

00:06:22.540 --> 00:06:23.699
your support.

00:06:24.579 --> 00:06:25.420
